iv class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"price\">Pick your Sahara Desert Tour wisely<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s quite a distance to the Sahara from Marrakech or Fes. But once you&#x2019;ve seen the sunset or the millions of stars at night, the journey is easily forgotten. The journey is also a beautiful part of the trip, and a great way to see more of Morocco&#x2019;s scenery!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Try to pick a tour that fits your itinerary, for example:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>How many days? It varies from 2 to 6 days<\/li><li>Are you leaving from Marrakech or Fes?<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-563x810.jpg\" alt=\"roads\"><\/noscript><img width=\"235\" height=\"338\" alt=\"roads\" class=\"wp-image-32338 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-563x810.jpg 563w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-300x431.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-600x863.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-417x600.jpg 417w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-235x338.jpg 235w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-1068x1536.jpg 1068w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114938\/roads-morocco-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2